ass=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellent support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/csdshop/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1bdaeab84c535abcfa93e4f3844fb7aa1edcfd9386be35784e3c0c53224c2859?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1bdaeab84c535abcfa93e4f3844fb7aa1edcfd9386be35784e3c0c53224c2859?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/csdshop/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Stefano <small>(csdshop)</small></a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng 4 2, 2026</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We had a problem on the button \"pubblish\", after an update we resolve it.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Thank you so much!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Fast and Super Helpful</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/christie212/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/10000f766551bf9f6d4ac690aa771e7c718210eccd6634cb68fa535fbb87e0ba?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/10000f766551bf9f6d4ac690aa771e7c718210eccd6634cb68fa535fbb87e0ba?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/christie212/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">christie212</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng 4 1, 2026</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Had a few problems with my site but Frank Remmy and Shahzeen were super helpful and replied quickly.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good but Heavy</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lizahamid/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8100921781351b6a49e75ece6e35d7f1b2644e71f67ce14a993e1bfcc963ad1f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8100921781351b6a49e75ece6e35d7f1b2644e71f67ce14a993e1bfcc963ad1f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/lizahamid/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">lizahamid</a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng 4 1, 2026</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Works well for online stores n has lots of features. But feels a bit heavy n setup takes time. Once done, it runs fine tho 👍</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Super fast support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 trên 5 sao\" data-title-template=\"%s trên 5 sao\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Bởi <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dziudek/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ec3db6152e60dd4ffbcaacd2b0af93ce81530d1f83781697380f5edf2f4ada96?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ec3db6152e60dd4ffbcaacd2b0af93ce81530d1f83781697380f5edf2f4ada96?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dziudek/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Tomasz Dziuda <small>(dziudek)</small></a> vào <span class=\"review-date\">Tháng 3 30, 2026</span>			</p>\